{"id":279268,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-江苏公民冯兰美就被非法拘禁申请行政复/","date":"2013-02-15T17:15:59Z","modified":"2013-02-15T17:15:59Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏公民冯兰美就被非法拘禁申请行政复议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，江苏省如皋市如城镇的冯兰美以特快邮寄方式，向江苏省南通工商行政管理局提交行政复议申请书。请求：依法撤销如皋工商行政管理局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>作出皋工商函字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">002</span><span>号信访答复，并责令其对冯兰美的举报依法处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>，冯兰美向如皋工商局举报苏通生态园向他人提供非法拘禁访民的场所，属于超范围经营，请予以查处。该工商局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>作出皋工商函字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">002</span><span>号信访答复，谎称：“党组高度重视，一把手局长印露当即批示辖区内城西分局进行调查取证。城西分局两名工商干部于次日即赴苏通生态园进行调查。……工商干部二次赴苏通生态园检查，均未发现其存在超范围经营的问题。”冯兰美认为，该答复并非重视公民的举报，而是绞尽脑汁对领导进行一番表彰。其错误明显：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>首先，冯兰美向工商局举报苏通生态园提供非法关押访民的场所，属于超范围经营。这是举报行为，而不是信访行为。因此，工商局按信访处理是错误的。其次，苏通生态园明知没有登记不能住宿，但为了得到非法经营利益，为他人提供非法拘禁的场所，明显属于超范围经营。该工商局竟然睁着眼睛说瞎话，称“工商干部二次赴苏通生态园检查，均未发现其存在超范围经营的问题”为此，冯兰美向江苏省南通工商行政管理局提起行政复议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日，冯兰美诉如皋市如城镇政府强拆民房案终于立案了。但才隔了一天，即</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，如皋地方政府国家工作人员为防止冯兰美上访，竟强行将冯兰美关进苏通生态园实施虐待，时常不准她睡觉，强迫她签订拆迁安置协议，还逼迫她撤诉，甚至威逼她写不上访的保证书，直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>才将冯兰美释放，非法拘禁达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>天。冯兰美表示，她要举报公务员滥用职权非法拘禁公民的违法行为，追究其法律责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qMwjRW8ivHw/UR5BE4e6v9I/AAAAAAAAdIU/22jPmtfYLkU/s1600/%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%86%AF%E5%85%B0%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qMwjRW8ivHw/UR5BE4e6v9I/AAAAAAAAdIU/22jPmtfYLkU/s320/%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%86%AF%E5%85%B0%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>关押冯兰美的黑监狱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QgseD59KLbE/UR5BH2RWlGI/AAAAAAAAdIc/5iWPM0JXx5w/s1600/0004.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QgseD59KLbE/UR5BH2RWlGI/AAAAAAAAdIc/5iWPM0JXx5w/s320/0004.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0a07F6HJdTw/UR5BH5Y-bHI/AAAAAAAAdIg/9hPohoMWVH0/s1600/0005.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0a07F6HJdTw/UR5BH5Y-bHI/AAAAAAAAdIg/9hPohoMWVH0/s320/0005.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\"